Maximizing  Efficiency and Liquidity



















Our Commitment

Citadel Securities is one of the world’s leading market makers across a broad array of fixed income and equity products. Our exceptional capabilities enable us to meet the liquidity demands of our diverse group of clients in most market conditions. In partnering with us, clients including asset managers, banks, broker-dealers, hedge funds, government entities, and public pension programs, are able to get better pricing and a more efficient trading experience. We are proud to help better position them to meet their investment and business goals.










