Begins delivery of algorithms to external clients











2012

Launches OTC and IMM market making business











2014

Launches Interest Rate Swap market making. Citadel Connect reaches 79m shares ADV2.











2015

Launches US Treasuries market making.

Recognized as “Interest Rate Derivatives House of the Year” by Risk Magazine and IFR Magazine. Wins “Best Electronic Liquidity Provider” at the Markets Choice Awards. Named one of the country’s 30 best workplaces in financial services and insurance by Great Place to Work.










2016

Becomes #1 Designated Market Maker on the NYSE

Becomes #1 Designated Market Maker on the NYSE3. Launches CDX market making. Wins “Rates and Equities Flow Market Maker of the Year” from Risk Magazine. 2016 also saw trading surges at critical historical moments, with Citadel Securities managing more than a 3x volume increase following the US election and over 4x during Brexit. Firm named one of the country’s 50 best workplaces for recent college graduates by Great Place to Work. Firm recognized as Best Flow House for Equities and Interest Rates by Risk Magazine.









 





