Organizations We Serve

We help our communities reach their full potential by creating meaningful, sustainable outcomes. We support more than 25 community partners, with a special focus on education, hunger and poverty relief, and cultural and medical organizations across the globe. While financial support is part of our effort, the heart of Citadel Serves is our employees’ commitment to sharing their time and expertise. Last year, our colleagues contributed more than 450 volunteer hours at events such as stocking food banks and building and delivering a child’s first bike to families in low-income communities.


























































 








